# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo
# tsc build-mode (`tsc -b`, e.g. from an IDE) emits these from the composite
# vite.config project reference (tsconfig.node.json). The plain `tsc` in
# `npm run build` doesn't, and the reference can't use `noEmit` (composite
# projects forbid it — TS6310), so ignore the artifacts here.
vite.config.js
vite.config.d.ts

